text.content: i had avoided this Bourne series in that and until now i gave it a shot because i was intrigued by a clip on internet about Bourne confronts the daughter of his victim from the past. but that part was not included in this first movie.

text.content: the movie was solid good, everything is ambiguity and confusing to me from start to end but the movie is engaging enough for me. the dynamic and chemistry between jason and marie is the highlight and i like it. however, to me something was still missing, something holds my expectation so high and i think because of the clip i watched on yt. i'm fine with it
